@startuml 06-seq-place-order
title Sequence — Place Order

actor Customer
participant "React SPA" as SPA
participant "Auth Middleware" as Auth
participant "Orders Service" as Orders
participant "Payment Service" as Payment
participant "Notifications Service" as Notif
database PostgreSQL
database Redis
participant Stripe

Customer -> SPA: Submit cart checkout
SPA -> Auth: POST /orders (JWT)
Auth -> Auth: Validate JWT
Auth -> Orders: Forward request

Orders -> PostgreSQL: BEGIN transaction
Orders -> PostgreSQL: SELECT stock FOR UPDATE
Orders -> PostgreSQL: Decrement stock
Orders -> PostgreSQL: INSERT order (PENDING)
Orders -> PostgreSQL: COMMIT

Orders -> Notif: Enqueue "order received" email
Notif -> Redis: LPUSH email job

Orders -> Payment: Create Payment Intent
Payment -> Stripe: POST /payment_intents
Stripe --> Payment: { client_secret }
Payment --> Orders: client_secret
Orders --> SPA: { orderId, client_secret }

SPA -> Stripe: Confirm payment (client-side)
@enduml
